<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="width:100%; background-color:#F5F5F9; padding: 50px;font-family: sans-serif; ">
        <div style="width:160px;  margin: auto; margin-bottom:20px ">
            <img src="https://www.portalferreirasantos.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/dummy-logo-5b.png"
                style=" margin: auto; display: inline-block; width: 160px;">
        </div>
        <div
            style="width:500px; background-color:white;    box-shadow: 2px 2px 6px 1px #302e330f; padding: 50px;font-family: sans-serif; margin: auto; ">
            <p style="font-family: sans-serif;">Hi Jane Doe,</p>
            <p style="font-family: sans-serif;line-height:1.4em;"> We've received a request to set a new password for
                this account: <b> algo@gmail.com. </b></p>
            <a
                style="background-color:#1a82e2; padding:10px 20px; display:inline-flex; color:white; font-family: sans-serif;border-radius: 3px; margin-top: 20px; cursor:pointer; width: fit-content;">Set
                password </a>
            <p style="margin: 0;text-align: center;font-size: medium;color: gray;">
                This token is only available for 30 minutes
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>